Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.64,0:00:05.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(632,538)}Hey, did you hear?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.10,0:00:11.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(646,542)}Two kids from our school participating in the World Duel Carnival made it to the tournament finals.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.86,0:00:16.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryoga-{\i1}sama{\i0} was a given, but I can't believe that kid also...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.32,0:00:17.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yup, yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.83,0:00:20.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, who was he again?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.33,0:00:22.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That kid with the catchphrase...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.12,0:00:23.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Um...\N - Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.29,0:00:27.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna bring it to 'em!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.68,0:00:36.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wanna autograph?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.72,0:00:38.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't hesitate to give our autographs!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.85,0:00:40.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-How about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.10,0:00:41.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My autograph!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.10,0:00:42.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give you my autograph!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.68,0:00:43.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lemme autograph!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.81,0:00:45.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll autograph for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.31,0:00:48.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't Tsukumo-{\i1}kun{\i0} getting a little full of himself?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.06,0:00:49.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.31,0:00:50.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.73,0:00:53.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To summarize, he's a braggart.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.03,0:00:55.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, c'om, lemme autograph!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.95,0:01:00.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That hurts, hurts, hurts, {\i1}hurts{\i0}, Kotori!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.41,0:01:02.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop showing off!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.75,0:01:05.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gosh...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.87,0:01:08.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You really are an idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.50,0:01:11.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I made it all the way to the finals, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.42,0:01:13.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me enjoy myself a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.96,0:01:15.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.13,0:01:16.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lookie here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.26,0:01:17.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take a look at this!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.84,0:01:19.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tada!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.01,0:01:20.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got me an official invitation!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.51,0:01:24.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The invitation to the Night Ceremony prior the Finals! It'll be held tonight at Heartland!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.27,0:01:25.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.39,0:01:26.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.98,0:01:29.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's got to be a lot of Dueling celebrities attending!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.65,0:01:32.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cat! What should I wear?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.11,0:01:37.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- This is exciting!\N - Hey! I'm the one who got invited!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.91,0:01:43.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just thought of a great plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.24,0:01:46.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not gonna let Yuma hog all the enjoyment!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.29,0:01:51.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The strongest Duelists from around the world have gathered.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.00,0:01:53.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They've come to fight it out in the World Duel Carnival.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.17,0:01:59.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I beat many guys and finally qualified for the tournament finals!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.51,0:02:01.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I don't care how strong they are! Bring 'em!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.60,0:02:03.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm gonna win the championship!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.43,0:02:05.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm gonna bring it to 'em!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.68,0:02:12.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Advance, advance, beyond the limits of your strength
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.02,0:02:18.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Come along with me and burn our flame of life
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.92,0:02:34.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hey, my friends, what scenery do you suppose
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.05,0:02:40.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}awaits us on the other side of this hill?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.51,0:02:45.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hey, my friends, let's climb it together
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.68,0:02:51.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's too late for us to turn back now
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.94,0:02:56.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The time has come to combine\N together the power dwelling inside me
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.19,0:03:01.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Gotta release my Soul Drive
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.78,0:03:07.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Advance, advance, beyond the limits of your strength
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.00,0:03:12.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Come along with me and burn our flame of life
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.38,0:03:18.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Keep running, keep running, until you get there
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.63,0:03:23.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Once again, once again, keep those challenges coming
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.05,0:03:30.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My friends, keep on living in the here and now
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.43,0:03:36.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Keep pressing onward together no matter what happens
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.00,0:03:59.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(459,493)}"Number 50: The Eve of the Storm!\N The Diabolical Duelist Appears - Tron!"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.23,0:04:12.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(643,526)}Wait, Tron.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.81,0:04:19.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Strengthen me, just like you did with III!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.36,0:04:23.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm disappointed in you and III.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.49,0:04:24.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wha...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.45,0:04:27.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why, you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.33,0:04:30.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, III fought...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.50,0:04:34.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...against the Original Number and ended up like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.58,0:04:36.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like he is right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.12,0:04:38.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want {\i1}results{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.71,0:04:43.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you guys are unable to do this, I have other options.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.47,0:04:45.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like Ryoga Kamishiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.84,0:04:50.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I dragged him into this tournament for that purpose.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.35,0:04:57.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why...?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.44,0:04:58.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why, Tron?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.01,0:05:24.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaito-{\i1}sama{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.97,0:05:26.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're at your limit!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.80,0:05:29.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you use Photon Mode anymore to search for Numbers,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.39,0:05:31.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,your recovery will take even longer!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.97,0:05:34.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You're pushing yourself far too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.93,0:05:37.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You sure that's a good idea, Kaito?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.60,0:05:40.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,K-Kaito-{\i1}sama{\i0}'s body is...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.31,0:05:42.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As you can see, it's not a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.11,0:05:44.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's good to hear.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.65,0:05:49.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now is the time to act, while the Numbers have been gathered in Heartland City.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.82,0:05:53.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We have high expectations for you, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.12,0:05:54.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.12,0:05:57.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you better help Haruto as you promised.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.29,0:06:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Of course. You needn't worry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.00,0:06:01.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Ah, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.63,0:06:04.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We'll be expecting you at tonight's ceremony.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.96,0:06:10.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Getting a glimpse of the Number Users beforehand may not be a bad idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.75,0:06:40.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, Heartland always looks so friggin' awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.38,0:06:44.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For real! It's so pretty!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.88,0:06:46.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cat!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.09,0:06:49.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kotori, you really went all out with that outfit.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.01,0:06:51.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As they say, "Chickens need feathers, people need clothes."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.93,0:06:53.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chicken?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.68,0:06:56.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yours suits you well too, Cat-{\i1}chan{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.47,0:06:58.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That Monster Cat cosplay of yours!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.14,0:06:58.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Monster?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.56,0:07:00.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's your problem?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.39,0:07:04.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it, you two. We managed to come to Heartland...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.57,0:07:08.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heartland...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.99,0:07:13.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This place was built by Dr. Faker.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.07,0:07:16.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A dreamland where everyone from children to adults can have fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.37,0:07:20.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Children who live in poverty are treated with priority.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.66,0:07:25.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When you think about it, such philosophy is praised worldwide.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.54,0:07:27.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The total area is...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.09,0:07:29.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How did you know all that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.01,0:07:32.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems that the Numbers obtained from III
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.09,0:07:36.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,contained the memory pieces of information about this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.05,0:07:40.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can’t help but to feel your top-to-bottom view has become even sharper…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.02,0:07:45.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This must be the party's assembly hall!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.98,0:07:48.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To summarize, it's a red carpet!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.69,0:07:51.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I kind of feel like a star.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.82,0:07:53.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Meow, meow~!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.45,0:07:54.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No means no!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.70,0:07:58.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those uninvolved are not permitted to enter!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.45,0:08:02.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got me an invitation right...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.50,0:08:03.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.50,0:08:04.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.92,0:08:09.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.63,0:08:11.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuma, you can't mean... again...?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.76,0:08:12.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You lost it...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.93,0:08:19.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I already said that I'm a finalist!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.97,0:08:25.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How can a kid like you be a finalist?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.40,0:08:26.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's true!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.94,0:08:29.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If so, show us your invitation!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.65,0:08:30.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.94,0:08:32.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now go on home.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.03,0:08:37.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything has a flip side.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.66,0:08:39.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tokunosuke?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.79,0:08:43.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I came up with an idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.79,0:08:47.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That’s the female Duelist, Milky Kulala!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.08,0:08:51.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even red carpets have a flip side.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.38,0:08:57.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I finally get the chance to wear a dress and it's ruined.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.39,0:09:00.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.19,0:09:12.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.74,0:09:17.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.61,0:09:18.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuma-{\i1}kun{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.28,0:09:19.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.04,0:09:26.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,God, you really are an idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.92,0:09:38.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll utilize Yuma and those idiots.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.34,0:09:40.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please give me your autograph!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.93,0:09:42.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a fan of yours!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.76,0:09:45.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's someone who qualified for the tournament finals...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.11,0:09:52.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.57,0:09:53.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.94,0:09:56.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You little prankster!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.70,0:09:59.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was wondering who it was, and it turned out to be Yuma Tsukumo.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.95,0:10:00.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.91,0:10:01.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gauche-{\i1}sama{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.66,0:10:03.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're making a big scene as always.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.83,0:10:05.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What'd you do this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.00,0:10:07.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, he came here without an invitation!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.66,0:10:12.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine. He may not look like it, but he's a final participant.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.46,0:10:14.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.88,0:10:18.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You feel like you can't believe me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.55,0:10:21.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No, sir...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.72,0:10:22.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.72,0:10:23.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.18,0:10:29.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whacha think? My mood's quite the...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.68,0:11:02.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-Amazing...!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.80,0:11:05.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That’s one of the finalists,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.47,0:11:08.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the Black Panther from the midst of South America, Garcia Panther!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.73,0:11:16.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On that side, it’s the white-night noble, Beroman Sakata!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.32,0:11:19.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-And...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.57,0:11:22.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Fallguys!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.86,0:11:24.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,During countless Duel Tournaments,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.66,0:11:29.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,this Dark Trio pushed their opponents to the abyss of terror with their overwhelming might!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.25,0:11:30.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Shark?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.91,0:11:32.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's here, isn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.00,0:11:35.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaito!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.46,0:11:38.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.30,0:11:44.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yuma Tsukumo... You are Kazuma-{\i0}san{\i1}'s son, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.47,0:11:47.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Your dad is alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.64,0:11:49.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In the Astral World.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.82,0:11:59.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's quite unusual coming from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.57,0:12:00.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Screw you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.94,0:12:02.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you put Haruto through that...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.45,0:12:04.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even you're my former mentor…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.66,0:12:06.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...you won't forgive me, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.41,0:12:11.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why...? Tell me why...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.45,0:12:13.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is your goal?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.37,0:12:17.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We merely obey Tron's will.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.25,0:12:18.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tron...?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.25,0:12:20.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You will meet him eventually.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.09,0:12:21.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me... he's in the finals?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.55,0:12:31.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you really think you'll defeat me and Tron with your body in this condition?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.33,0:12:50.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're gone...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.83,0:12:54.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to ask him something...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.62,0:12:56.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, here you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.96,0:12:58.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're next, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.67,0:12:59.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.34,0:13:02.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fanservice is my motto, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.89,0:13:09.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Move!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.22,0:13:11.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're in my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.70,0:13:26.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.74,0:13:29.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's your usual insults?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.79,0:13:35.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The time I've been waiting for is almost here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.37,0:13:38.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will bet everything I have to defeat you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.94,0:13:58.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You look stressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.52,0:14:02.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Droite...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.94,0:14:06.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been able to tell something's wrong with you for a while now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.24,0:14:07.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.57,0:14:10.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I received word from the medical room.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.91,0:14:12.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your body is already...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.99,0:14:14.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've got bad taste.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.16,0:14:18.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's unfortunate about Haruto.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.46,0:14:22.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know you have to collect Numbers at all costs.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.42,0:14:23.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.63,0:14:26.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't enter the finals.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.63,0:14:28.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no reason to listen to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.93,0:14:30.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaito!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.84,0:14:32.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,V is in the finals...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.43,0:14:35.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's now with this man named Tron who kidnapped Haruto.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.64,0:14:36.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaito!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.72,0:14:38.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Above all else, I won't...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.60,0:14:42.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...lose against that guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.77,0:14:45.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just thinking about you...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.07,0:14:55.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You showed me quite the night ceremony befitting what is to come.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.74,0:14:59.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the fruit of our steadily progressing plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.21,0:15:01.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Has the main cast been gathered?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.92,0:15:05.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All but one have shown up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.25,0:15:06.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.21,0:15:09.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A Duelist disguising himself as Tron.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.34,0:15:10.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tron?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.47,0:15:11.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does that ring any bells?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.09,0:15:13.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.93,0:15:17.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I, as the representative of Heartland,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.93,0:15:21.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,will deliver the reception speech to the finalists.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.11,0:15:31.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To summarize, Tokunosuke-{\i1}kun{\i0} didn't come inside with all of us?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.15,0:15:33.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't see him anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.82,0:15:36.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could you be...?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.99,0:15:43.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To summarize, you're the powerful Duelist, The Vampire of Dawn, Lord of Terror Nagashima!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.00,0:15:46.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To summarize...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.09,0:15:49.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please give me your autograph!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.51,0:15:52.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Class Rep loves collecting his autographs.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.31,0:15:58.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.89,0:16:04.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Flip the flip side!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.94,0:16:05.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Flip?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.87,0:16:21.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heart Burning!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.25,0:16:27.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ladies and gentleman!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.75,0:16:30.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And all present Duelists!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.80,0:16:34.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you enjoying the party?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.43,0:16:43.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Starting tomorrow, the Duel Carnival finally reaches the Final!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.60,0:16:49.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please allow me to reintroduce the remaining 23 warriors!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.40,0:16:51.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.92,0:17:14.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wha-What the?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.40,0:17:38.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, what a big cake!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.50,0:17:54.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And y-you are...?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.46,0:17:55.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Tron!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.13,0:17:59.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Call me Tron.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.26,0:18:01.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tron...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.93,0:18:03.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's...Tron?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.35,0:18:10.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gramps...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.15,0:18:13.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.86,0:18:16.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is something the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.86,0:18:21.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gramps, I'm gonna...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.32,0:18:23.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...crush you guys into the ground!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.88,0:18:33.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, I {\i1}love{\i0} cake!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.63,0:18:38.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, the kid down there!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.30,0:18:42.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's meet in the finals.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.48,0:18:58.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can see me, can't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.38,0:19:14.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.17,0:19:15.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.25,0:19:17.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? Where'd he go?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.05,0:19:18.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.21,0:19:20.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just what is he...?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.64,0:19:28.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Over there! It's him! Him!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.85,0:19:31.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My impostor!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.03,0:19:44.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.58,0:19:51.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys did it again, huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.25,0:19:52.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No we didn't!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.08,0:19:56.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.98,0:20:13.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To summarize, it was Tokunosuke-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.02,0:20:15.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's what he meant when he said flip the flip side!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.40,0:20:17.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Wait up!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.98,0:20:21.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I said you've got it wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.43,0:20:50.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tron...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.70,0:21:10.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is Haruto okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.95,0:21:13.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have no reason to be worried about him.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.75,0:21:16.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just focus on settling the score with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.42,0:21:18.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaito...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.09,0:21:21.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will give it my all.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.30,0:21:22.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Same here, man!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.96,0:21:24.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get the wrong idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.55,0:21:27.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not going to give my all to defeat {\i1}you{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.68,0:21:28.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I meant {\i1}Astral{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.93,0:21:32.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Darn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.91,0:21:52.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you're going to hire us or something, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.95,0:21:53.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.66,0:21:56.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're expensive.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.25,0:22:00.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then we'll start with a small deposit.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.96,0:22:03.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The rest comes when you complete your job.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.30,0:22:07.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the target is...?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.17,0:22:09.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A boy named Yuma Tsukumo.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.51,0:22:13.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Got 'em!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.60,0:22:25.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We stand tall, until we have victory in our grasp
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.99,0:22:31.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Move on ahead, speeding up our throbbing beats
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.00,0:22:42.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Listen boys and girls, here's the secret to boys and girls like you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.46,0:22:46.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You're really just so spontaneous, wild as can be
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.34,0:22:47.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I bet you didn't know?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.88,0:22:50.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You might be a handful, but what's wrong with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.47,0:22:52.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Be up to no good, but learn for real
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.10,0:22:58.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Go the unpredictable route and shuffle your cards with a goal in mind
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.35,0:23:03.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Whenever you feel like you've lost your way, just take a minute to close your eyes...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.61,0:23:09.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Shout "stop!" with all you've got, and there's your boundary line.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.49,0:23:15.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We stand tall, until we have victory in our grasp
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.79,0:23:21.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We won't just stop here, not when we don't want to have any regrets.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.29,0:23:26.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even if we get hurt, we can't just hesitate now
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.59,0:23:31.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We won't just give up, not when our future's a lot brighter than our today
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.97,0:23:37.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Seriousness... It'll only make us keep fighting even harder
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.43,0:23:42.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We'll always get as fascinated as we want, and we'll fight on every day
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.03,0:23:53.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Duel Carnival Tournament Finals have finally begun!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.66,0:23:57.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s the final battle between the strongest Duelists who qualified for the Final!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.66,0:23:59.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Duel Coasters?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.08,0:24:01.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, sounds like fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.46,0:24:02.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.50,0:24:05.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There might be some unknown strong opponents among them!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.29,0:24:07.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? It's gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.17,0:24:08.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My Heart Pieces are gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.84,0:24:10.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuma, it's coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.13,0:24:12.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time on Yu-Gi-Oh! ZeXal!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.84,0:24:16.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Here we come, Tournament Finals! Duel Coasters, Go!"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.35,0:24:18.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A three-on-one Duel?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.23,0:24:24.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Today we're introducing Heroic Champion Excalibur!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.31,0:24:26.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Its effect doubles its Attack Power.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.27,0:24:27.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It can save you in a pinch.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.69,0:24:28.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I got no need for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.98,0:24:31.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you forgotten the time you and Kaito were in a pinch?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.49,0:24:33.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll permit a Tsukumo Pinch!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.36,0:24:34.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like heck I will!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.32,0:24:36.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
